text: Gustavo Ramos Hernández (born 16 June 1974) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
